	depends on LGE_LCD_TUNING
	bool "Dynamic Log"
	default y
	---help---
	If you say Y here, developers can enable/disable display logs through adb
	by accessing /sys/class/graphics/fb0/debug_level
	ex. echo {debug_level} > sys/class/graphics/fb0/debug_level

